---
const features = [

  {
    id: 'faq-1',
    question: 'Why choose Burrowin Electrical for Gold Coast electrical services?',
    answer: 'Burrowin Electrical stands out as your trusted Gold Coast electrician, offering top-notch residential and commercial electrical solutions. With a commitment to quality and safety, we ensure your electrical needs are met with expertise and reliability.',
  },
  {
    id: 'faq-2',
    question: 'What areas on the Gold Coast does Burrowin Electrical service?',
    answer: 'Our services cover the entire Gold Coast region, ensuring residents and businesses across suburbs receive prompt and professional electrical assistance. From Surfers Paradise to Robina, we\'ve got you covered.',
  },
  {
    id: 'faq-3',
    question: 'Are emergency electrical services available with Burrowin Electrical?',
    answer: 'Yes, Burrowin Electrical provides 24/7 emergency electrical services on the Gold Coast. Whether it\'s a sudden outage or an urgent repair, our team is ready to address your electrical emergencies promptly.',
  },
  {
    id: 'faq-4',
    question: 'Can Burrowin Electrical help with residential electrical upgrades on the Gold Coast?',
    answer: 'Absolutely! We specialize in residential electrical upgrades across the Gold Coast. From lighting installations to panel upgrades, our skilled electricians enhance your home\'s safety and functionality.',
  },
  {
    id: 'faq-5',
    question: 'What commercial electrical services does Burrowin Electrical offer in Gold Coast?',
    answer: 'Burrowin Electrical caters to a wide range of commercial electrical needs on the Gold Coast, including office wiring, lighting solutions, and electrical maintenance. Trust us for efficient and business-friendly electrical solutions.',
  },
  {
    id: 'faq-6',
    question: 'Are Burrowin Electrical\'s services compliant with Gold Coast electrical regulations?',
    answer: 'Yes, our services strictly adhere to Gold Coast electrical regulations and standards. Burrowin Electrical prioritizes safety and compliance to ensure your electrical systems meet all legal requirements.',
  },
  {
    id: 'faq-7',
    question: 'How can I request a quote for electrical services from Burrowin Electrical on the Gold Coast?',
    answer: 'Requesting a quote is easy! Simply visit our website or give us a call. We provide transparent and competitive quotes for all our electrical services on the Gold Coast.',
  },
  {
    id: 'faq-8',
    question: 'Does Burrowin Electrical offer energy-efficient solutions for Gold Coast homes and businesses?',
    answer: 'Yes, we specialize in energy-efficient electrical solutions tailored for Gold Coast properties. From LED lighting installations to energy-efficient appliance recommendations, we help you save on your energy bills.',
  },
  {
    id: 'faq-9',
    question: 'Can Burrowin Electrical assist with electrical renovations in Gold Coast homes?',
    answer: 'Certainly! Burrowin Electrical is your go-to partner for electrical renovations on the Gold Coast. We collaborate seamlessly with renovation projects, ensuring your electrical systems align perfectly with your upgraded spaces.',
  },
  {
    id: 'faq-10',
    question: 'What steps should I take during a power outage before contacting Burrowin Electrical on the Gold Coast?',
    answer: 'In the event of a power outage, first, check if your neighbors are also affected. If it\'s a localized issue, contact your electricity provider. If the problem persists, call Burrowin Electrical for prompt assistance, and we\'ll diagnose and resolve the issue efficiently.',
  },
  
];
---

<section class="my-28">
  <div class="mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 w-full lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-8">
      <h4 id="components" class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight pt-2">FAQ's</h4>
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <dl
          class="-mt-3"
          x-data="{ selected: null, toggle(value) { this.selected = this.selected === value ? null : value } }"
        >
          {
            features.map((feature, index) => (
              <div
                class="rounded-3xl px-4 transition"
                x-data={`{ id: ${index}, get isOpen() { return this.id === this.selected }, get isNextOpen() { return (this.id + 1) === this.selected } }`}
                x-bind:class="{ 'bg-primary-500/10 dark:bg-primary-400/10': isOpen }"
              >
                <dt
                  class="border-b text-lg transition"
                  x-cloak
                  x-bind:class="{ 'border-transparent': isOpen || isNextOpen, 'border-primary-900/10 dark:border-primary-300/10': !(isOpen || isNextOpen) }"
                >
                  <button
                    type="button"
                    class="group block w-full py-6 text-left transition focus-visible:outline-none"
                    aria-controls={feature.id}
                    x-on:click="toggle(id)"
                    aria-expanded="false"
                    x-bind:aria-expanded="isOpen.toString()"
                  >
                    <div class="group-focus-visible:outline-primary-950 dark:group-focus-visible:outline-primary-200 flex items-center justify-between rounded-3xl group-focus-visible:outline group-focus-visible:outline-2 group-focus-visible:outline-offset-2">
                      <span class="text-lg md:text-xl font-medium">{feature.question}</span>
                      <span class="ml-6 flex h-7 items-center">
                        <svg
                          class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 h-6 w-6 rotate-0 transform transition duration-200 ease-in-out"
                          x-bind:class="{ '-rotate-180': isOpen, 'rotate-0': !isOpen }"
                          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                          fill="currentColor"
                          aria-hidden="true"
                        >
                          <path d="M11.9997 13.1714L16.9495 8.22168L18.3637 9.63589L11.9997 15.9999L5.63574 9.63589L7.04996 8.22168L11.9997 13.1714Z" />
                        </svg>
                      </span>
                    </div>
                  </button>
                </dt>
                <dd class="pb-6 pr-6" id={feature.id} x-show="isOpen" x-cloak x-collapse>
                  <p class="text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 text-base xs:text-lg">
                    {feature.answer}
                  </p>
                </dd>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
